ld be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide all tokens to the users."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It implements also the protocol ","type":"text"},{"code":"RadioButtonComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to expose the component tokens for ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"radio buttons","type":"text"}]},{"text":" through any ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Radio buttons"}]},{"text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"SizeSemanticToken","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":") and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"borders (","type":"text"},{"code":"BorderRadiusSemanticToken","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"code":"BorderWidthSemanticToken","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":").","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"These components share the same type of tokens which are all gathered here.","type":"text"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeRadioButtonComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"title":"Theme Orange","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","images":[{"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"icon"}],"type":"topic","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"}}}